Variable.Name: v_GCGTOConnectionCapacities
Variable.Description: Maps every gridconnection to the calculated contribution to a GTO (Groep Transport Overeenkomst). Delivery and FeedIn respectively.

Variable.Name: c_presentations
Variable.Description: Would have to be filled by hand with all presentations that are (indirectly) on the interface canvas. eg: c_presentations.add(uI_Tabs_presentation)
